oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: William Strickland plan of altar for the Second Presbyterian Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Plate 55 of a collection of seventy-three original drawings by William Strickland. The sketch shows elevation and plans for the altar and choir loft of the Second Presbyterian Church. It is signed by Strickland.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Strickland, William, 1787-1854
